window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I’m James Thorne—Level 25 Psyker Apex—and I’m bouncing back from a pretty catastrophic battle on Rithos.</b> The thing is, I’m stranded deep within a hostile jungle crawling with things that want to eat me.</p> <p>With Darius Cylis dead and the Crusade shattered, survival now hinges on my ability to leverage every skill, stat, and system exploit I can muster.</p> <p>Hunted by Emperor Arkanar’s forces, my team battles dwindling mana reserves, critical health levels, and an environment where even the shadows deal damage.</p> <p>I’m going to survive this jungle. I’m going to survive the Emperor. And I’m absolutely not going down quietly.</p> <p>Because Marines don’t die easy—they just come back meaner.</p>"; 
